node.text:
It's always fun getting to sample a moonshine corn whiskey. Seeing what unaged distillate tastes like gives you a sense of a the potential of a distillery. In this case, the heavy buttered popcorn flavor profile in this @copperskylongmont moonshine corn whiskey has us excited to dive into their aged whiskey products 🥃
